				<h1 id="research">Research Interests</h1>
				<div class="descr">Aug 12, 2009</div>

				<p>Although I'm interested in a lot of areas, currently, I'm concentrating on Computer Architecture and Embedded Systems.</p>

				<ul>
					<li class="toplevel"><b>Computer Architecture</b>: Prefetcher, Memory Hierarchy, High-Performance Computing, Multi-Core System</li>
					<li class="toplevel"><b>Embedded Systems</b>: System Architecture, System Security</li>
				</ul>


